OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson ruled unfit to stand
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FLady Eleanor Donaldson, the wife of
OL,7,Fthe former DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson, has been ruled unfit to
OL,9,Fstand trial on historical sexual
OL,10,Foffences.
OL,12,FJudge Paul Ramsey made the ruling at
OL,13,FNewry Crown Court on Wednesday after
OL,14,Fhearing medical evidence.
OL,16,FThe judge told the court: "I am
OL,17,Fsatisfied that upon the totality of
OL,18,Fthe evidence presented I will
OL,19,Fdetermine that Eleanor Donaldson is
OL,20,Funfit to be tried."
OL,26,@xD@[OU|D@SO]
