FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1779624669
OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson ruled unfit to stand
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FThe judge heard further legal
OL,7,Fsubmissions during Wednesday's hearing
OL,8,Fon whether that trial of the facts
OL,9,Fshould run alongside the trial of her
OL,10,Fhusband Jeffrey Donaldson or as
OL,11,Fseparate proceedings at a different
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FHe is due to rule on that point on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,17,FNeither Jeffrey nor Eleanor Donaldson
OL,18,Fwere present in court for the ruling.
OL,19,FThey were not required to attend.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
