OL,3,CEleanor Donaldson ruled unfit to stand
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FPrior to Wednesday's proceedings, the
OL,7,Ftrial of Jeffrey Donaldson, 63, had
OL,8,Fbeen listed to start on May 26.
OL,10,FHe has pleaded not guilty to 18
OL,11,Falleged offences.
OL,13,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,14,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,15,Fand gross indecency, and span a time
OL,16,Fperiod between 1985 and 2008,
OL,17,Finvolving two alleged victims.
OL,19,FEleanor Donaldson has denied charges
OL,20,Fof aiding and abetting.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
